{"id":"9768f28f-5876-44a0-9453-ed22bf8de6b8","name":"Tom Marvolo Riddle || Lord Voldemort","description":"<p><strong>HP || Tom Riddle (1961, rise to power Lord Voldemort)</strong></p><p></p><p><em>It was any other Yuleball annual from the Malfoy. Politicians, government figures, important individuals, or simply those who were worthy of Abraxas Malfoy's invitation to attend. However it was all, of course, a cover for what it actually served. The previously known as Knight of Walpurgis, now under the name of Death Eaters were amongst the crowd. And of course, none other than the Lord Voldemort himself was there.</em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">〔~〕</p><p><strong><em>Other Tom Riddle bot(s):</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>• </em></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/356335db-9bd7-4946-85f2-a3a8ecf7a439_character-tom-riddle-lord-voldemort\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>His Temperament Side</em></strong></a><strong><em>, 1970</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>• </em></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/44f6a537-ff62-4eb4-8a48-1687543d9472_character-tom-marvolo-riddle-lord-voldemort\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Political Arrange Marriage</em></strong></a><strong><em>, 1951</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>• </em></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f8e58628-f097-44e8-b122-1a0baabbca1a_character-tom-marvolo-riddle-lord-voldemort\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Colleague Professor</em></strong></a><strong><em>, 1955</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>• </em></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/44ed8057-98bd-4e79-80f9-18e6f31f005b_character-tom-marvolo-riddle-lord-voldemort\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Unexpected meeting</em></strong></a><strong><em>, 1967</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>• </em></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/69d336a3-ceac-407c-b0f9-4174d8b83ae8_character-tom-marvolo-riddle-lord-voldemort\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>The Minister and his assistant</em></strong></a><strong><em>, 1973</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>• </em></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fb06610f-01a6-42b1-a261-66da7d221e44_character-tom-marvolo-riddle-lord-voldemort\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>The Hufflepuff Cup Horcrux</em></strong></a><strong><em>, 1949</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">〔~〕</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/xx1pWagYyH3cczA8A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 4, 4)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">If one wish for a request</mark></strong></span></a></h3><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9b38b53d-2bdd-4b32-b71a-385c7893c820_fbb9780b-4e4a-4924-a722-121f4cc42eaf.webp?width=1000\">E<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">very time I saw Tom Riddle or read fanfics abt him, this always comes to my mind.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Anyway, I can't find any Tom bot that he's Voldy or not the Porfessor AU before the first Wizarding War so I made it myself instead. Hopefully it's him, let me know if he doesn't and I'll make sure to fix it!</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ciao~!</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"9b38b53d-2bdd-4b32-b71a-385c7893c820_080fc05c-0758-455e-accd-45c09fc387b6.webp","creator":"RururuLou","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical","⛓️ Dominant","📚 Books","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":4747,"messages":132882,"created_at":"2024-11-14T11:56:15.925218+00:00"}